# ── Local dev (browser) ────────────────────────────────────
# Leave empty. Vite proxies /api → http://localhost:3001
# Run from repo root: npm run dev

# ── Capacitor native (release build) ───────────────────────
# Optional — bundled apps auto-use Railway if unset.
# Emulator against local API:
# VITE_API_URL=http://10.0.2.2:3001
# VITE_GOV_API_BASE_URL=http://10.0.2.2:8001/api/v1

# ── Vercel (optional override) ───────────────────────────
# RAILWAY_API_URL=https://bigtits-api-production.up.railway.app

# ── Optional: direct browser → Railway (skip Vercel proxy) ─
# VITE_API_URL=https://bigtits-api-production.up.railway.app